    public class ConcatenatedList<T>
extends AbstractList<T>
    A list made by joining multiple sublists of Ts together. A ConcatenatedList can be created using create(java.util.List) or create(java.util.List[])
    Since:
    API 4.60 (Geneious 5.6.0)
